title: Week 1 of College Football, Khalil Mack dealt to the Bears,and Jim Harbaugh's Michigan
itunes:title: Week 1 of College Football, Khalil Mack dealt to the Bears,and Jim Harbaugh's Michigan
description:
Doug Gottlieb fills in for Colin and thinks Raiders head coach Jon Gruden did a great job trading Khalil Mack for 2 first round picks. He argues people are overreacting to Michigan losing to Notre Dame and why Jim Harbaugh won't be going anywhere. Doug talks to Danny Kanell from CBS Sports to find out if Michigan can recover from their week 1 loss and still make the College Football Playoff.  Guests Include: Danny Kanell, Clay Travis, and Nick Baumgardner
